  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基础设施的调用流程图，核心是从Etcd集群开始，先经过Ingress控制器做流量入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Etcd作为起点，然后连到Ingress控制器。这个Ingress控制器后面是怎么分叉的？我看代码里它有两条出边。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Ingress控制器要分成两条路径：一条通过chain关系走到LoadBalancer，另一条通过attestation回到Etcd集群做校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "chain和attestation，两个不同的关系标签。那LoadBalancer后面接什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "LoadBalancer后面挂到WorkerNode，同时Etcd集群也要直接连到WorkerNode，形成汇聚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把WorkerNode做成菱形判断节点，前面两条线汇进来。接下来WorkerNode怎么展开？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WorkerNode这里要做个条件分支：yes走Redis缓存，no的话回退到LoadBalancer做重试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "yes去Redis，no回LoadBalancer。Redis之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Redis后面要再连回Etcd集群，但这里Etcd要变成判断节点，区分self-hosted和SaaS两种部署模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这个Etcd集群前面已经出现过一次了，现在又要作为判断节点出现，是同一个节点还是新的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
