    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "是新的判断节点，虽然都是Etcd，但这里专门用来做部署模式的分支判断，逻辑上独立。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "了解，我标记为H节点。self-hosted分支指向WorkerNode，SaaS分支指向LoadBalancer，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
