      "utterance": "收到，F到H无标签。整个流程：Etcd→Ingress→(chain)LoadBalancer↘，Ingress→(attestation)Etcd↘，两者汇聚到WorkerNode→(yes)Redis→Etcd判断→self-hosted/WorkerNode或SaaS/LoadBalancer，以及WorkerNode→(no)LoadBalancer。结构对吗？",
